WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.200
An easy way to increase your score and make more money is by referring people to Tradewize.

2
00:00:06.200 --> 00:00:10.000
Click the Refer a Friend icon on the homepage.

3
00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:13.600
Simply click Share with friends and enter their email.

4
00:00:13.600 --> 00:00:18.000
If they apply and start jobs, you'll earn points and be rewarded.

5
00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:22.900
Everyone you have referred will show up on a list under your referred friends.

6
00:00:22.900 --> 00:00:29.000
You are able to see their name, start date, status, how many jobs they have completed,

7
00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:31.000
and their total score.

8
00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:38.500
There is no limit to how many people you can refer, so please send this link to as many people as possible.

9
00:00:38.500 --> 00:00:45.000
Building our network will create more jobs and more income for everyone who does quality work.